column4: NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "49F2CD46472C95617219F3881B726200", "Talk to Tsunomon and Yuramon as often as you can.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "13CE0CCA42AFFBE7696292A9FE5EEFD2", "I\'ll tell you about the Tamer level.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "A758F03C44B74B4D924D6BBC6D254B11", "With a high Tamer level, when your Digimon fades away,")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "EC5C992C434A5E61DDA4E3B253D20725", "your next Digimon will have better parameters.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "F9926AC54C6AFF2F7551D09A7301E3E4", "In the beginning it won\'t go up much,")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "5AC819DA41C46E69219F0388028FD36A", "but keep steadily raising him and it will get better.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "424CA612410C556B32775BB2F5FB7A83", "When you use your Finishing Technique, make sure to rapidly hit L and R buttons.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "DDBB6F494D21F2A76EDA1E8755994AFA", "When Finish Gauge is full, compared to when empty, the damage to enemy is double!")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "F2C339C4460B00DD5559CA9EE1C2134D", "I\'ll tell you about a Digimon\'s life.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "215C40004D63998B7B29838928D62684", "When Digimon gets hungry, he\'ll tell you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "C02951004D27C0163B3FCEA6026C22DC", "He also needs to go potty. Make sure he does it in the toilet.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "3CCBAA904B2E32200F3A72841CEDF9DA", "Digimon get sleepy and need sleep, but you have to make him sleep.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "34154BC34D9B0C50A6DC10833DA3CA5A", "Don\'t try to keep him up for too long.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "365D90904B5C0991F5EB0EA833B95C3B", "He may get tired, sick or just get upset. He\'s kinda delicate.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "CC0973E446ABD66A22AC47AA6A5CE2D5", "Since Digimon are wild creatures, you should praise or scold them.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7260490843274BABF740C29EBA0E36E0]", "586F13ED4EAAC2836DE3A6B14259CE54", "Whatever you do, pay attention to what your Digimon is doing.")
